Interface SootMethodInterface

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SootMethodRef
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PolymorphicMethodRef, SootMethod, SootMethodRefImpl

    public interface SootMethodInterface
    The common interface of SootMethod (resolved method) and SootMethodRef (unresolved method). Therefore it allows to access the properties independently whether the method is a resolved one or not.
